{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/membuat-post-baru-di-jekyll/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>Post ini ialah post lanjutan dari post <a href=\"/memasang-jekyll-di-ubuntu\">Memasang Jekyll di Ubuntu 18.04 Bionic dan Turunannya</a>, untuk membuat post di Jekyll pertama - tama yang harus disiapkan yaitu menginisiasi Jekyll di folder kerja web/blog terlebih dahulu. Masukkan perintah berikut ke terminal :</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">jekyll new nama-web-blog</code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 659px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/6f3d8cd74edcce46cf1be8a015201da1/6db71/new-post-1.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 68.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"screenshot 1\"\n        title=\"screenshot 1\"\n        src=\"/static/6f3d8cd74edcce46cf1be8a015201da1/6db71/new-post-1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/6f3d8cd74edcce46cf1be8a015201da1/772e8/new-post-1.png 200w,\n/static/6f3d8cd74edcce46cf1be8a015201da1/e17e5/new-post-1.png 400w,\n/static/6f3d8cd74edcce46cf1be8a015201da1/6db71/new-post-1.png 659w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 659px) 100vw, 659px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Ganti <code class=\"language-text\">nama-web-blog</code> dengan yang lain. Kemudian masuk ke folder baru dan mulai server Jekyll.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token builtin class-name\">cd</span> nama-web-blog\njekyll serve</code></pre></div>\n<p>Jekyll akan memulai server di <a href=\"http://localhost:4000\">http://localhost:4000</a>. Buka untuk melihat web yang baru dibuat.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/dd5c36221237087f060f83a85b7be393/77abb/new-post-2.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 50%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"screenshot 2\"\n        title=\"screenshot 2\"\n        src=\"/static/dd5c36221237087f060f83a85b7be393/5a190/new-post-2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/dd5c36221237087f060f83a85b7be393/772e8/new-post-2.png 200w,\n/static/dd5c36221237087f060f83a85b7be393/e17e5/new-post-2.png 400w,\n/static/dd5c36221237087f060f83a85b7be393/5a190/new-post-2.png 800w,\n/static/dd5c36221237087f060f83a85b7be393/c1b63/new-post-2.png 1200w,\n/static/dd5c36221237087f060f83a85b7be393/77abb/new-post-2.png 1305w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3>Membuat Post</h3>\n<p>Untuk membuat post, buat file baru di folder <code class=\"language-text\">_posts</code> pada folder kerja web Jekyll. Sebelum menuliskan konten terlebih dahulu buat <code class=\"language-text\">front matter</code>, ini ialah bagian yang harus ada dalam setiap post di Jekyll. Isinya berupa keterangan -keterangan yang diawali oleh tiga symbol <code class=\"language-text\">-</code> juga diakhiri dengan tiga symbol tersebut. Jika bingung Jekyll telah membuat post awal di folder yang sama dengan format <code class=\"language-text\">.markdown</code> yang bisa disalin front matter-nya dan disesuaikan sesuai kebutuhan. Baru setelah ada front matter konten bisa ditulis. Post di Jekyll normalnya ditulis dengan format <code class=\"language-text\">markdown</code>, seluk beluk dan cara menulis markdown dapat dibaca di web <a href=\"https://www.petanikode.com/markdown-pemula/\">petanikode</a>.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/964b6694a2575968150baa1a48f0e9b9/ad00e/new-post-3.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 55.99999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"screenshot 3\"\n        title=\"screenshot 3\"\n        src=\"/static/964b6694a2575968150baa1a48f0e9b9/5a190/new-post-3.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/964b6694a2575968150baa1a48f0e9b9/772e8/new-post-3.png 200w,\n/static/964b6694a2575968150baa1a48f0e9b9/e17e5/new-post-3.png 400w,\n/static/964b6694a2575968150baa1a48f0e9b9/5a190/new-post-3.png 800w,\n/static/964b6694a2575968150baa1a48f0e9b9/c1b63/new-post-3.png 1200w,\n/static/964b6694a2575968150baa1a48f0e9b9/ad00e/new-post-3.png 1366w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 797px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/60797990ff50e74d9dbf20157561e040/43fbc/new-post-4.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 66%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"screenshot 4\"\n        title=\"screenshot 4\"\n        src=\"/static/60797990ff50e74d9dbf20157561e040/43fbc/new-post-4.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/60797990ff50e74d9dbf20157561e040/772e8/new-post-4.png 200w,\n/static/60797990ff50e74d9dbf20157561e040/e17e5/new-post-4.png 400w,\n/static/60797990ff50e74d9dbf20157561e040/43fbc/new-post-4.png 797w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 797px) 100vw, 797px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Simpan file baru dengan format nama <code class=\"language-text\">YYYY-MM-DD-judul-posts</code> dan format <code class=\"language-text\">.markdown</code>.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/de805982466079ffad0b8b20a2a99c67/46e30/new-post-5.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 50%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"screenshot 5\"\n        title=\"screenshot 5\"\n        src=\"/static/de805982466079ffad0b8b20a2a99c67/5a190/new-post-5.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/de805982466079ffad0b8b20a2a99c67/772e8/new-post-5.png 200w,\n/static/de805982466079ffad0b8b20a2a99c67/e17e5/new-post-5.png 400w,\n/static/de805982466079ffad0b8b20a2a99c67/5a190/new-post-5.png 800w,\n/static/de805982466079ffad0b8b20a2a99c67/c1b63/new-post-5.png 1200w,\n/static/de805982466079ffad0b8b20a2a99c67/46e30/new-post-5.png 1303w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Selesai, untuk melihat post baru buka kembali <a href=\"http://localhost:4000\">http://localhost:4000</a>, tapi pastikan server Jekyll telah dimulai.</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Membuat Post baru di Jekyll"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/membuat-post-baru-di-jekyll/"}}}